DISCLAIMER ON THEORETICAL CLAIMS
---------------------------------
The "Unsolved Problems" demonstrations contained in the Algorithms/UnsolvedProblems/
directory are theoretical proposals and conceptual explorations of post-quantum
computing paradigms. They are NOT proofs of mathematical theorems and make no
claim to having solved problems that are established open questions in classical
computer science and mathematics. These demonstrations are provided for research
inspiration and academic discussion purposes only.

The benchmark results in Algorithms/Benchmarks/ reflect theoretical post-quantum
complexity analysis and simulation outputs. They do not represent benchmarks
performed on physical quantum hardware.
